---
---

<section class="px-6 py-20">
  <div
    class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-zec-surface border border-zec-border rounded-2xl p-10 text-center space-y-6"
  >
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zec-text">Ready to run your node?</h2>
    <p class="text-zec-muted max-w-lg mx-auto">
      macOS 12+ required. Apple Silicon and Intel supported. The Zcash
      blockchain needs approximately 300 GB of free disk space.
    </p>
    <a
      href="https://github.com/stefanmirrors/zecbox/releases/latest"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg bg-zec-yellow text-zec-dark font-semibold text-lg hover:brightness-110 transition-all"
    >
      <svg
        class="w-5 h-5"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      >
        <path
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          stroke-width="2"
          d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"
        ></path>
      </svg>
      Download .dmg
    </a>
    <p class="text-sm text-zec-muted max-w-md mx-auto">
      macOS may show a security warning for unsigned apps. Right-click zecbox in
      Applications, select Open, then click Open again.
    </p>
    <p class="text-xs text-zec-muted">
      Windows and Linux coming soon.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
